## Phase 4 — Tree-Based Retrieval Intelligence

**Goal:** Layer a hierarchical domain classifier on top of vector search to narrow the search space before embedding similarity runs, reducing noise and improving precision.

### 4.1 Domain Tree

```
Root
├── faculty
│   ├── industry_energy
│   │   ├── information_technology
