## Phase 2 — Vector Database Integration

**Goal:** Replace TF-IDF with semantic embeddings stored in ChromaDB. ChromaDB runs locally (embedded mode for dev, server mode for prod) with zero cloud dependency.

### 2.1 Technology Choice

| Component | Selection | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Vector DB | **ChromaDB** (`chromadb` npm client) | Node.js native client, runs local, free, production-ready |
| Embeddings | **Nomic Embed** via Ollama (local) _or_ **Voyage AI** (cloud) | Ollama = zero cost; Voyage = better quality |
